                        <p>Best chefs in America <a href="http://www.jamesbeard.org/awards/aruns-2010-334">read more</a></p>


                        <header>
                            <h2>Chicago Reader</h2>
                            <h4 class="serif">• August 2001 • Laura Levy Shatkin</h4>
                        </header>

                        <p>Critics and diners agree -- you haven't experienced Thai food until you've let Arun Sampanthavivat seduce you with his sophisticated fare. Arun's brings Thai cuisine to new heights, using only the freshest ingredients in tantalizing combinations plated so exquisitely that it's almost vandalism when you dig in.</p>

